### 获取所有博客
GET http://localhost:3000/api/blogs

### 创建新博客
POST http://localhost:3000/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Blog 123",
  "author": "John Doe",
  "url": "https://example.com/new-blog",
  "likes": 5,
  "userId": "6865d7df06219a09fe600647"
}

